    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c0b4e-102"><xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentDirection>枚举表示要在其中显示容器控件中包含文本的控件的方向。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0b4e-102">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentDirection> enumeration represents the direction in which to display controls that include text in a container control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c0b4e-103">控件，如<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>和<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>控件，具有属性，用于<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentDirection>枚举值来指定要在其中显示子控件的方向包含文本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0b4e-103">Controls, such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls, have properties that use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentDirection> enumeration values to specify the direction in which to display child controls that include text.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c0b4e-104">如果指定 LeftToRight 值，包含文本的子控件将显示从左到右对齐的容器控件左侧文本的文本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0b4e-104">If you specify the LeftToRight value, child controls that include text display text from left to right and justify the text on the left side of the container control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c0b4e-105">如果指定 RightToLeft 值，包含文本的子控件将显示从右到左的文本和文本在容器控件的右侧对齐。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0b4e-105">If you specify the RightToLeft value, child controls that include text display text from right to left and justify the text on the right side of the container control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c0b4e-106">RightToLeft 值用于显示的语言编写从右到左，如阿拉伯语和希伯莱语的文本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0b4e-106">Use the RightToLeft value to display text for languages that are written from right to left, such as Arabic and Hebrew.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c0b4e-107">下面的代码示例演示如何使用<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentDirection.LeftToRight>枚举可设置<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.Direction%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0b4e-107">The following code example demonstrates how to use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentDirection.LeftToRight> enumeration to set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.Direction%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c0b4e-108">A<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListBox>控件中填充<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentDirection>枚举值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0b4e-108">A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListBox> control is populated with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentDirection> enumeration values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c0b4e-109">中基于用户从列表框中选择的值的面板更改的标签和单选按钮的显示方向。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0b4e-109">The display direction of the label and radio buttons in the panel change based on the value that the user selects from the list box.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c0b4e-110">由于本示例使用英文文本选择 RightToLeft 值之后的右侧对齐文本<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.Direction%2A>维护控件，但英文文本的左到右的顺序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0b4e-110">Because this example uses English text, when the RightToLeft value is selected, the text is justified on the right side of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.Direction%2A> control, but the left-to-right order of the English text is maintained.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c0b4e-111">在实际应用中，则不要设置<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.Direction%2A>属性 RightToLeft 值，如果您要显示使用左到右的顺序的语言的文本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0b4e-111">In a real-world application, you would not set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.Direction%2A> property to the RightToLeft value, if you were displaying text for a language that uses left-to-right order.</span></span>  
  
